{"tid":1435911,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"去年底已暗交？姜丹尼爾戴志效手織頸巾襲港","createTime":"2019-08-09T07:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T11:56:35.000Z","uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9326fdde81e1d20970c9181ab094d3a396351783","tid":1435911,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190809/photo/bkn-20190809111532741-0809_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190809115225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190809%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190809111532741-0809_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190809115225&h=f4705390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姜丹尼爾的灰色頸巾疑是志效（右下圖）親手織，TWICE隊友亦有同款頸巾。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190809/photo/bkn-20190809111532741-0809_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190809115225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190809%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190809111532741-0809_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190809115225&h=ac6efab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE隊友曾在官方社交網答謝志效為她們親手織頸巾。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190809/photo/bkn-20190809111532741-0809_00862_001_07p.jpg?20190809115225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190809%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190809111532741-0809_00862_001_07p.jpg%3F20190809115225&h=444d01c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姜丹尼爾去年12月來港出席《MAMA》，圍上的灰色頸巾疑是志效親手織。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190809/photo/bkn-20190809111532741-0809_00862_001_08p.jpg?20190809115225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190809%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190809111532741-0809_00862_001_08p.jpg%3F20190809115225&h=a7580a09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n志效被拍得多次到姜丹尼爾的寓所約會。<br />\n<br />\n限定韓團Wanna One的22歲前成員姜丹尼爾，本周一被爆暗撻人氣女團TWICE隊長志效，二人大方認愛，但有粉絲表明不再支持他，網上出現大量負評。<br />\n<br />\n二人的戀情曝光後，有網民發現姜丹尼爾去年12月10日生日後，出發來港參加《MAMA音樂頒獎禮》，現身首爾機場時，圍着的灰色頸巾疑是志效親手編織，並上傳相關照片，包括TWICE隊友曾在官方社交網上傳機場的照片，並留言答謝志效：「雖然很害怕冬天，但圍上志效織的頸巾會不會暖一點」照片中隊友圍上的灰色頸巾跟姜丹尼爾那條一樣。據悉姜丹尼爾於去年底，透過圈中前輩2AM出身的瑟雍介紹認識志效，二人於年初開始交往。<br />\n<br />\n而姜丹尼爾於昨晚透過事務所官方YouTube頻道，公開新碟《Color on me》收錄曲《I HOPE》的排舞片段，並於今日向首爾地方警署網絡犯罪搜查隊提出控告網上發放虛假、含侮辱及人身攻擊等惡意留言的網民，涉侮辱罪、誹謗及損害其名譽。"},{"pid":"b80804effc5a2c7e26428103cc50eec9d59b924d","tid":1435911,"uid":555,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:28:42.000Z","msg":"落地獄"},{"pid":"4a8c8aaba73792467d5eca6f429b63f7a217926a","tid":1435911,"uid":294712,"like":19,"dislike":6,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"去年底已性交 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a386fb11480175c0a93529cbf73a172aba28f5","tid":1435911,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4a8c8aaba73792467d5eca6f429b63f7a217926a","tid":1435911,"uid":294712,"like":19,"dislike":6,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"去年底已性交 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"都呃得我地ONCE透啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b830cfc0739765ddedbec7ec0fc45252606b0a","tid":1435911,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:34:45.000Z","msg":"去年底...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5007b08650b559b14fa10c600f1c1f35fd30f204","tid":1435911,"uid":60256,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:40:43.000Z","msg":"如果以一周性交一次計算，大山婆已經被中出差唔多40次"},{"pid":"cc68a3ca602d6f14400b4ca72bbf5f09f90b8a40","tid":1435911,"uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5007b08